  "text": ". We look for proportional periodic waves in the form φ = (ϕ(x − ct), ϕ(x − ct)). Hence, (1.5) can be rewritten as 2) ]. In particular the existence of periodic solutions for (3.17) may be obtained as in [CITATION_1] . For the convenience of the reader we recall the result below.",
